n educational module\nin particle physics data analysis for high school students and teachers. Here,\nwe introduce ADL and CutLang and present the educational activities based on\nthese practical tools.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 24 Mar 2022 19:00:07 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-03-28"}
