 are much\nsimpler to be realized than others found in the literature and the best design\nachieves a high thermal emission power with a tunable range on the order of 132\nW/m2.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 24 Mar 2022 18:23:05 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-06-10"}
